If you do not receive timely acknowledgment of your complaint, or if your complaint is not satisfactorily addressed by Circuit ID, please visit the BBB EU SAFE HARBOR web site at http://www.bbb.org/us/safe-harbor-complaints for 
more information and to file a complaint.
